programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: Seorang asisten profesor mencuri mikrofilm yang menyimpan rahasia reaktor nuklir nan baru ditemukan dan menjualnya ke suatu sindikat kejahatan. Namun, benda itu jatuh ke tangan penari klub malam dan seorang pencuri.

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: Sekuel dari The Empress Dowager ini melanjutkan kisah Kaisar Guangxu dan Ibu Suri Cixi. Terlepas dari penobatan Guangxu sebagai raja, kemampuannya untuk memerintah secara efektif dibayangi oleh kekuatan Cixi.

programme.title: Martial Club
programme.desc: Wong Fei Hung muda dan temannya Wang Yin Lin mendapati keduanya dan sekolah seni bela diri mereka berseteru dengan sekolah saingan lain dan Guru Shan, ahli bela diri yang mereka pekerjakan.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: Ling Yun berperan sebagai pemain pengganti yang disewa oleh sebuah band populer setelah pemain drum mereka yang egois mengundurkan diri untuk bergabung dengan band saingan mereka.

programme.title: My Rebellious Son
programme.desc: Alexander Fu Sheng berperan dalam film komedi laga sebagai anak ceroboh yang harus berhenti menguji kemampuan sang ayah dan berjuang bersamanya untuk memerangi seorang pejabat korup.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Film komedi romantis yang dibintangi artis legendaris Lin Feng Jiao ini menceritakan kisah cinta yang tak biasa antara putra seorang pengusaha dan keponakan perempuan dari seorang kepala sekolah taman kanak-kanak.

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Salah satu drama seni bela diri yang paling digandrungi sepanjang masa, menceritakan tentang Sekte Pembunuhan Tiga Belas Elang dari klan Perahu Besi dan para prajurit tangguh yang dipersatukan oleh tragedi.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: Big Potato membuka sebuah klinik Tiongkok kuno, namun metode tradisionalnya ditolak oleh masyarakat Hong Kong modern yang skeptis. Ia meminta sahabatnya, Mr. Funnybone, untuk membantu menyelamatkan kliniknya.

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor's Power
programme.desc: Penguasa terakhir dinasti Tang, Li Yao, digulingkan oleh Chao Kuang-jun, pendiri Dinasti Sung. Sayangnya, tindakannya tersebut menimbulkan kekacauan baru di pengadilan dan masyarakat.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: Peter Chen Ho is the suave playboy gallivanting across Asia, while having his way with three unsuspecting sisters, setting in motion a parade of mishaps and comic interludes.

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses.

programme.title: Martial Arts Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers' death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate.

programme.title: Sword Stained With Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from the novel by Jin Yong, havoc breaks out when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, training manual, treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased master.

programme.title: Whose Baby Is In The Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls' high school, is stuck with a baby that isn't his and must take care of it. His class helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching.

programme.title: Notorious Eight
programme.desc: More than a gambling film, this is the story of Chen, looking to avenge his father's death and recoup his debts, through a blazing combination of martial arts and nail-biting action.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jin's daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love.

programme.title: Cat Vs Rat
programme.desc: When young martial artist 'The Rat' unwittingly rescues the emperor from a gang of thieves, it sets in motion a chain of events that see him compete for his life against 'The Cat'.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps.

programme.title: Ode To Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly lighthearted 'Venoms' martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer (Kuo Chue) is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: An amusing insider's look at the Hong Kong film industry from Li Han Hsiang, recreating some of the era's funniest and most surreal stories ripped straight from the gossip.

programme.title: Holy Flame Of The Martial World
programme.desc: A massive hit both at home and overseas, this tells the story of an orphaned brother and sister who study the mystical Holy Flame kung-fu technique to avenge their parents' deaths.

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: This is a story of adolescent playfulness and innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together, but rivalry intervenes when they discover boys!

programme.title: The Lady Professional
programme.desc: Lily Ho stars as a seductive hit woman in this contemporary Shaw Bros action thriller. Filmed in HK and Japan the story follows Ho's assassin as she discovers she is now a target.

programme.title: Blue Skies
programme.desc: Cheng Pei-pei stars as a young singer, Hsiao-Yun, struggles between her success in career and her relationship with her pianist lover Li Yen-nan.

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: In this classic tale of brotherhood and heroism, a psychotic young man (David Chiang) sets out on a bloody trail of vengeance after the untimely death of his older brother (Ti Lung).

programme.title: The Blue And The Black, Pt 2
programme.desc: Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and report to officials, while heroes emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: Three girls travel to Japan to collect an unexpected inheritance, only to be met by three guys there to do the same. So begins a vicious battle to receive what was promised them.

programme.title: The Flag Of Iron
programme.desc: The Flag of Iron, a righteous clan, is in confrontation with the Eagles Society which covers up illicit operations.

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title refers to two props that signal a happy beginning to what develops into a tragic love story between the scholar and a local beauty.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Master Tie Qiao San is an honorable and respected kung fu master, one of the Ten Tigers of Kwantung. He's also developed a bit of a taste for opium, though, and his habit is getting worse.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxing
programme.desc: Chan and his apprentice Fan transport vampires for a living. When two of them hopped away, it is revealed that one of them is actually a man in disguise trying to escape from his enemies.

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks and forcing a pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant.

programme.title: River Of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her.

programme.title: House Of Traps
programme.desc: From the great Chang Cheh comes this highly sought after action spectacular about a team of skilled fighters navigating a house rigged with an array of ingenious and deadly traps.

programme.title: Return Of The Dead
programme.desc: Enchanted Shadow is about three stories. A husband and wife that discover they should be careful what they wish for, a naked female ghost seeks revenge and a dead prostitute returns as a ghost in the last tale.

programme.title: Purple Darts
programme.desc: A girl vows to take revenge for her parents who were murdered by four outlaws when she was only a baby. To do so, she trains hard at martial arts and teams up with a swordsman and a couple to finally kill them all.

programme.title: 2020 Idol Star Athletics, Ep 6
programme.desc: Kejuaraan kali ini diisi oleh sejumlah grup idola Korea terkenal yang menunjukkan sportivitas mereka. Empat puluh empat tim termasuk SEVENTEEN, MONSTA X, MOMOLAND, dan SF9 akan bertanding di berbagai cabang olahraga!

programme.title: The Barber Of Seville, Ep 5
programme.desc: Para penata rambut terbaik di Korea mengunjungi Sevilla di Spanyol untuk menjalankan salon rambut. Saksikan apakah mereka berhasil memikat hati pelanggan setempat dengan beberapa teknik andalan mereka.

programme.title: Iron Squad S2, Ep 6
programme.desc: Acara bertahan hidup militer Korea ini menampilkan delapan unit Pasukan Khusus yang bersaing dalam sejumlah misi ekstrem yang akan menguji stamina fisik, kekuatan mental, dan kerja tim mereka!

programme.title: Yacht Expedition, Ep 4

Serta mengarahkan anak-anak untuk mengeksplorasi kehidupan yang bermakna, membantu mereka fokus pada tugas yang ada dan belajar mengelola emosi yang mengganggu mereka.

programme.title: THE SMURF
programme.desc: Di tengah hutan belantara, terdapat desa rahasia dihuni oleh sekelompok makhluk kecil berwarna biru yang dipimpin oleh Papa Smurf. Kedatangan penyihir jahat Gargamel dan kucingnya, Azrael, merusak kedamaian desa tersebut. Sehingga para Smurf harus mencari cara agar tidak ditangkap oleh Gargamel dan Azrael

programme.title: NUSSA
programme.desc: Serial animasi karya anak Indonesia yang mengisahkan tentang kehidupan Nussa, anak laki-laki periang yang bercita-cita menjadi Astronot yang Tahfidz Qur'an. Nussa memiliki seorang adik yang riang dan menggemaskan, Rara. Di setiap episode Nussa, Rara, beserta teman-temannya akan memberi contoh perilaku sesuai ajaran agama Islam.

programme.title: ADIT SOPO JARWO
programme.desc: Animasi Indonesia, berisikan kisah kehidupan sehari-hari masyarakat Indonesia yang dipenuhi dengan pengetahuan, kelucuan, kisah persahabatan, serta nilai persatuan, kesatuan, dan kebudayaan. Tokoh dalam cerita ini diantaranya Adit, Adelya, Dennis, Mitha, Devi, Bang Sopo & Bang Jarwo, serta masih banyak lagi

programme.title: TAKDIR CINTA KERA SAKTI
programme.desc: 500 tahun yang lalu, Zi Xia turun ke bumi untuk menemukan Zhi Zun Bao, kekasihnya yang berhasil mengeluarkan pedang Zi Qing. Seiring berjalannya waktu, pedang Zi Qing rusak. Untuk memperbaikinya, Zi Xia menggunakan Kotak Pandora untuk menjelajah waktu, yang membuatnya terjebak di masa 500 tahun mendatang. Di sana ia bertemu Zhi Zun Bao, namun ia samasekali tidak ingat akan masa lalunya. Selain tidak ingat akan masa lalunya, ia sekarang adalah pemimpin kelompok pemberontak Bernama Ax Gang.
